  "description": [
   "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
   "  CH.02 · ON HORSES",
   "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
   "",
   "▸ The horse doesn't care about your quest.",
   "  But it runs faster than you.",
   "  And it carries the weight while you think.",
   "",
   "◈ HORSE MECHANICS",
   "  └ Taming: approach unmounted, keep mounting",
   "    until hearts appear — feed apples/sugar/hay",
   "  └ Breeding: golden apples or golden carrots",
   "    to speed-breed for better stats",
   "  └ Horse Armor: iron/gold/diamond — reduces damage",
   "  └ Chest: attach with lead while riding",
   "",
   "◈ TRAVEL BONUS",
   "  └ Via Romana roads give +speed while riding",
   "  └ A horse on a stone road is the Ch02 fast travel",
   "  └ Ch07 introduces Small Ships for water routes",
   "",
   "◈ SCROLL: On Horses",
   "  └ Found in: stable loot, village outpost chests,",
   "    rider supply crates, road waypoint ruins",
   "  └ Research time: 10 min",
   "  └ Unlocks: mounted travel awareness,",
   "    Via Romana road interaction knowledge",
   "",
   "▶ Find the On Horses scroll [check]",
   "▶ Obtain a Saddle",
   "▶ Tame a horse [check]",
   "",
   "◇ A tamed horse follows the player if on a lead.",
   "  Build a stable. Name it. It remembers."
